'''阿马里伊·贝尔'''（{{lang-en|'''Amari'i Bell'''}}，{{bd|1994年|5月5日|catIdx=Bell, Amari'i}}）是一名[[牙買加|牙買加]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[後衛_(足球)|左邊衛]]，現效力笊[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]。

==球會生涯==
阿马里伊·贝尔出身於[[索利赫尔沼泽足球俱乐部|索利赫尔沼泽]]的青訓系統，在2011年成為伯明翰青年軍一員<ref name=Extends>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/amarii-extends-stay-836466.aspx |title=Amari'i extends stay |author=Walker, Andy |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=28 May 2013 |accessdate=29 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221223552/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/amarii-extends-stay-836466.aspx |archivedate=2014年2月21日 }}</ref>，2012年6月與伯明翰簽下一年職業合約<ref name=TurnsPro>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-amarii-bell-signs-187216 |title=Birmingham City: Amari'i Bell signs senior contract |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=20 June 2012 |accessdate=29 January 2014 |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218000238/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-amarii-bell-signs-187216 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012/13球季，他成為發展隊的常規成員，並在季後獲得另一份伙期一年的合約，另加一年行使權<ref name=Extends/>。

2013年7月，貝爾被外借至[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|英議聯]]球會[[紐尼頓鎮足球會|紐尼頓鎮]]至2014年1月<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23247739 |title=Amari'i Bell: Nuneaton Town sign Birmingham City defender |publisher=BBC Sport |date=9 July 2013 |accessdate=29 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310202429/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23247739 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並成球季首場比賽上場，以1-0小勝[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|马科斯菲尔德]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nuneaton-news.co.uk/Sport/Nuneaton-Town-FC/Macclesfield-Town-0-Nuneaton-Town-1-match-report-analysis-and-ratings-20130812080029.htm |title=Macclesfield Town 0, Nuneaton Town 1 |author=Davies, Matt |newspaper=Nuneaton News |date=12 August 2013 |accessdate=29 January 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。由於母會缺乏防守球員參加[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]，因此他在9月20日被球會召回<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nuneaton-news.co.uk/Sport/Nuneaton-Town-FC/Nuneaton-Town-lose-Amarii-Bell-after-he-is-recalled-by-Birmingham-City-20092013.htm |title=Nuneaton Town lose Amari'i Bell after he is recalled by Birmingham City |author=Davies, Matt |newspaper=Nuneaton News |date=20 September 2013 |accessdate=29 January 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。回隊伯明翰後他雖獲發球衣號碼，但沒有上場比賽，數天後又外借到紐尼頓鎮<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20130926-bell-back-at-nuneaton-1078786.aspx |title=Bell back at Nuneaton |author=Walker, Andy |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=27 September 2013 |accessdate=29 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023035947/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20130926-bell-back-at-nuneaton-1078786.aspx |archivedate=2013年10月23日 }}</ref>。由於伯明翰左後衛[[米切·漢科斯|米切·漢科斯]]受傷及[[大卫·墨菲|大卫·墨菲]]倦勤，伯明翰在12月9日再次召回他<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-putting-faith-young-6389196 |title=Birmingham City putting their faith in teenage talent |author=Evans, Gregg |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=10 December 2013 |accessdate=29 January 2014 |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218000303/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-putting-faith-young-6389196 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年1月28日，貝爾首次代表伯明翰上場參加對[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]的比賽，換入受傷的漢科斯，球隊以2-1落敗<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/fixtures-results/match-report/index.aspx?matchid=3632207 |title=The Report: Blues 1 Leicester City 2 |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=28 January 2014 |accessdate=29 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221223756/http://www.bcfc.com/fixtures-results/match-report/index.aspx?matchid=3632207 |archivedate=2014年2月21日 }}</ref>。之後再沒有上場機會，因此在3月6日他被外借到[[京达米士特足球俱乐部|京达米士特]]至季末.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.harriers.co.uk/news/article/140306-amarii-1402196.aspx |title=Whild makes Bell first signing |publisher=Kidderminster Harriers F.C |date=6 March 2014 |accessdate=6 March 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306201722/http://www.harriers.co.uk/news/article/140306-amarii-1402196.aspx |archivedate=2014-03-06}}</ref>。4月15日對[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|剑桥联]]一戰，他打進職業生涯首顆進球，使球隊以2-0取勝<ref name=sb1314>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=70917&season_id=143 |title=Games played by Amari Bell in 2013/2014 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=27 April 2014 |archive-date=2020-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404193524/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=70917&season_id=143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014/15球季開始前，貝爾被外借到英乙球會[[曼斯菲尔德城足球俱乐部|曼斯菲尔德城]]至2015年1月<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28229150 |title=Amari'i Bell: Mansfield sign Birmingham defender on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=9 July 2014 |accessdate=9 July 2014 |archive-date=2014-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716111729/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28229150 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，三場比賽均沒有上場機會後便被召回<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mansfieldtown.net/news/article/blues-recall-bell-1836129.aspx |title=Blues recall Bell |publisher=Mansfield Town F.C |date=18 August 2014 |accessdate=18 August 2014 |archive-date=2016-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624085454/http://www.mansfieldtown.net/news/article/blues-recall-bell-1836129.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年9月26日，他外借到英甲球會[[斯温登足球俱乐部|斯温登]]至2015年1月31日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140922-swindon-loan-move-for-bell-1934249.aspx |title=Swindon loan move for Bell |first=Andy |last=Walker |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=26 September 2014 |accessdate=26 September 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140926220657/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140922-swindon-loan-move-for-bell-1934249.aspx |archivedate=2014年9月26日 }}</ref>，2015年3月外借到[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|吉林汉姆]]至季末<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31969528 |title=Amari'i Bell: Gillingham sign Birmingham defender on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=20 March 2015 |accessdate=21 March 2015 |archive-date=2015-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324064651/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31969528 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季末，伯明翰會方決定不行使合約延長權，宣佈放棄貝爾<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/amarii-bell-birmingham-city-2458910.aspx |title=Amari'i Bell released by Blues |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=18 May 2015 |accessdate=18 May 2015 |archive-date=2016-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920200713/http://www.bcfc.com//news/article/amarii-bell-birmingham-city-2458910.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管有傳吉林汉姆有意簽下他<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kentonline.co.uk/medway/sport/freebie-bell-could-tempt-gills-37155/ |title=Gillingham could make a move for full-back Amari'i Bell after Birmingham City announced he was being released |3= |first=Luke |last=Cawdell |website=Kent Online |date=19 May 2015 |accessdate=20 May 2015 |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218000352/https://www.kentonline.co.uk/medway/sport/freebie-bell-could-tempt-gills-37155/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他決定加盟英甲球會[[弗利特伍德镇足球俱乐部|弗利特伍德]]<ref name=SignsFleetwood>{{cite web |url=http://www.fleetwoodtownfc.com/news/article/fleetwood-town-football-club-amarii-bell-birmingham-city.-2464919.aspx |title=Fleetwood Town swoop for Bell |publisher=Fleetwood Town F.C. |date=20 May 2015 |accessdate=20 May 2015 |archive-date=2016-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630140038/http://www.fleetwoodtownfc.com//news/article/fleetwood-town-football-club-amarii-bell-birmingham-city.-2464919.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

貝爾於2018年1月19日與當時另一英甲球會布力般流浪簽約兩年半。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11676/11214068/blackburn-announce-amarii-bell-signing-on-two-and-a-half-year-deal|title=Blackburn announce Amari'i Bell signing on two-and-a-half-year deal|newspaper=Sky Sports|accessdate=2018-11-15|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129155243/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11676/11214068/blackburn-announce-amarii-bell-signing-on-two-and-a-half-year-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>

